AGRICULTURE CODE

offense under another provision of law, the person may be prosecuted
under either this section or the other provision.
(e) If conduct that constitutes an offense under this section
also constitutes a felony under Section 28.03 or 31.03, Penal Code,
the actor may be prosecuted only under Section 28.03 or 31.03, Penal
Code.
Added by Acts 2021, 87th Leg., R.S., Ch. 997 (H.B. 1480), Sec. 1, eff.
September 1, 2021.

